More than 20 Members of the Bundestag (MdB) attended the hearing, which included experts from NGOs, representatives of minority groups, and scholars.

David Li, a researcher with China Organ Harvest Research Center (COHRC), was invited to introduce the center’s findings. snippet.textDisplay: As far as the Keaton "surprise"...it was inevitable.  For years there's been talk about  the original version of The Sinister Six. I remember them talking about that when Garfield portrayed Spiderman. To my recollection, the only Sinister Six character that has not been introduced is Kraven the Hunter. Doc Oc was in Tobey's, Electro was in Andrew's, Mysterio was in Tom's, Sandman was in Toby's and Vulture was in Tom's and now Morbius. So Kraven the Hunter will have to be in this movie in order to proceed with the theory on The Sinister Six. I know props from the Sinister Six also appeared at the end of Garfield's Spiderman 2...Vulture's wings, Doc's arms and Kraven's spear. But with the changing of the Spiderman guard once again, will they keep it the way it was or start a new with the introduction of The Hobgoblin and Gog....
